'''Film Authors' Studio''' ({{lang-hr|Filmski autorski studio}}, '''FAS''') was a short-lived but influential<ref name="Goulding"/> [[Croatia]]n film production studio. Established in 1967, it was the first independent feature film production company in [[Yugoslavia]].<ref name="kinotuskanac"/>

