'''El Khabar Broadcasting Company''' ({{lang-ar|هيئة الخبر للإذاعة و التّلفزيون}}), or simply '''KBC''' ({{lang-ar|قناة الخبر}}), is an [[List of television channels in Algeria|Algerian private television channel]], owned by El Khabar Group. It was set up in December 25, 2013 by Ali Djerri, and is headquartered in the city of [[Algiers]].

==History==
KBC TV was founded on 25 December 2013, it has started to broadcast its programs on 25 December 2013. In May 2014, the [[United States Ambassador to Algeria|Ambassador of the United States in Algeria]] Henry S. Ensher visited the headquarters of the channel in [[Algiers]].

